                        <div class="editorBody">
                                <div class="nameGroup">
                                        <h3>Dr Matija Cuk </h3>
                                        <p>SETI Institute </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="details">
                                            <p><strong>Biography</strong></p>

<p>Matija&nbsp;Ćuk is Research Scientist at the SETI Institute in Mountain View, California. He specialises in the orbital and rotational dynamics of the Solar System bodies, and has worked on the origin and dynamics of binary asteroids, the Earth-Moon system, and Saturn's moons and rings. He is recipient of the 2014 Harold Urey Prize awarded by the Division of Planetary Sciences of the American Astronomical Society.</p>
 
                                            
                                                                                       
                                                <p><a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1226-7960"><img alt="ORCID logo" src="https://orcid.org/sites/default/files/images/orcid_16x16.png">https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1226-7960</a></p>
                                            
